Info - 
Raigadala Jevha Jaag Yete which translates into "When Raigad Fort Comes To Life" is a best superhit historic full stage play written by renowned marathi author Vasant Kanetkar. Raigadala Jevha Jaag Yete is based on the complex relationship between Shivaji Maharaj & his son Sambhaji. The actors are Mohan Joshi, Rujuta Deshmukh, Swati & Avinash Deshmukh. 

Directed by Anil Joglekar. 
Music by Anand Modak. 
Singer: Ravindra Sathe.
